title: (x) Rebirth Museum Logo - Elston {Stephen}
content:
Hey guys,

Does anyone have any guesses on what typeface this is? It looks quite similar to Neo Sans, but it’s more refined. I appreciate the help.

Mason

comments.content: [Elston](http://web.archive.org/web/20081121131043/http:/www.fontshop.com/fonts/singles/red_rooster/elston_light/?sample_text=REBIRTH%20MUSEUM&sample_size=60) - without even a modification of its extra tight spacing.
Hah! Nice one, thanks a bunch.
